title: #048 - When Life Gives You Lemons & On Aiming For Excellence
itunes:title: #048 - When Life Gives You Lemons & On Aiming For Excellence
description:
This week’s episode is one of those sweet solo episodes where I speak from the heart, totally unfiltered, and just share what’s on my mind.

This week, I share what it’s been like to come off the tail end of an intense launch of The School of Killer Impressions AND I share how I’ve been finding inspiration from Olympic Athletes.
